Christel Coetzer, a lover of literature, never dreamed that she would get married in a bookstore. On Saturday, 08 October 2016 that dream came true when she married her sweetheart, Etienne, at Skoobs Theatre of Books in Monte Casino, Johannesburg. The couple had their first date at the store and Etienne eventually proposed to Christel there. Three months later they decided to tie the knot at the same magical venue. All together now - ncaw!  